                    alt="Sith" /></a>
        </figure>
        <blockquote>
            "The dark side of the Force is a pathway to many abilities some
            consider to be...unnatural."
        </blockquote>
        <p>― Darth Sidious</p>
        <br />
        <p>
            The <strong>Sith</strong>, also referred to as the
            <strong>Sith Order</strong>, was an ancient religious order of
            Force-wielders devoted to the dark side of the Force. Driven by
            their emotions, including hate, anger, and greed, the Sith were
            deceptive and obsessed with gaining power no matter the cost. The
            order reached the apex of its power under Darth Sidious, the Dark
            Lord of the Sith who achieved his order's goal of galactic
            conquest after a millennium of plotting. Within a generation,
            however, the deaths of Sidious and Darth Vader would mark the end
            of the order of Sith Lords.
        </p>
    </div>
</article>

